# 🚀 Inventory Management & Order Processing System

A production-ready full-stack Inventory & Order Management System built using modern industry-standard technologies.

This application enables businesses to efficiently manage:

* 📦 Products
* 👥 Customers
* 📋 Orders
* 📊 Inventory Tracking

The project follows:

* RESTful API architecture
* Containerized deployment strategy
* Cloud deployment best practices
* Scalable backend design principles

---

# 🌐 Live Deployment Links

## 🖥️ Frontend Application

https://inventory-management-application-two.vercel.app/

## ⚡ Backend API

https://inventory-backend-jyub.onrender.com/

## 📚 Swagger API Documentation

https://inventory-backend-jyub.onrender.com/docs#/

## 🐳 Docker Hub Image

