# ✨ Core Features

## 📦 Product Management

* Create Products
* View Products
* Update Products
* Delete Products
* Inventory Quantity Tracking
* Unique SKU Validation

## 👥 Customer Management

* Add Customers
* View Customer Records
* Delete Customers
* Unique Email Validation

## 📋 Order Management

* Create Orders
* Track Orders
* Automatic Stock Deduction
* Inventory Validation
* Dynamic Total Price Calculation

## 📊 Dashboard Analytics

* Total Products
* Registered Customers
* Total Orders
* Low Stock Alerts

---

# 🛠️ Technology Stack

| Layer            | Technology              |
| ---------------- | ----------------------- |
| Frontend         | React.js + Tailwind CSS |
| Backend          | FastAPI                 |
| Database         | PostgreSQL              |
| ORM              | SQLAlchemy              |
| API Validation   | Pydantic                |
| Containerization | Docker                  |
| Orchestration    | Docker Compose          |
| Deployment       | Render + Vercel         |

---

# 🏗️ Project Architecture

```bash
inventory-system/
│
├── backend/                          # FastAPI Backend Service
│   │
│   ├── app/                          # Core backend application logic
│   │   │
│   │   ├── main.py                   # Main FastAPI application & API routes
│   │   ├── database.py               # Database engine & session management
│   │   ├── models.py                 # SQLAlchemy ORM database models
│   │   ├── schemas.py                # Pydantic request/response schemas
│   │   └── __pycache__/              # Python cache files
│   │
│   ├── Dockerfile                    # Backend container configuration
│   ├── requirements.txt              # Python dependencies
│   └── benv/                         # Local Python virtual environment
│
├── frontend/                         # React Frontend Application
│   │
│   ├── public/                       # Static frontend assets
│   │   ├── index.html                # Main HTML entrypoint
│   │   ├── favicon.ico               # Browser favicon
│   │   └── manifest.json             # Progressive Web App manifest
│   │
│   ├── src/                          # Frontend source code
│   │   │
│   │   ├── App.js                    # Main React application component
│   │   ├── App.css                   # Component styling
│   │   ├── index.js                  # React rendering entrypoint
│   │   ├── index.css                 # Tailwind global styles
│   │   ├── reportWebVitals.js        # Performance analytics setup
│   │   └── setupTests.js             # Frontend testing setup
│   │
│   ├── Dockerfile                    # Frontend container configuration
│   ├── tailwind.config.js            # Tailwind CSS configuration
│   ├── postcss.config.js             # PostCSS build configuration
│   ├── package.json                  # Node.js dependencies & scripts
│   ├── package-lock.json             # Dependency version locking
│   ├── README.md                     # Frontend documentation
│   └── node_modules/                 # Installed frontend packages
│
├── docker-compose.yml                # Multi-container orchestration
├── .gitignore                        # Git ignored files & directories
└── README.md                         # Project documentation
```

---

# 🐳 Docker Setup

## Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/adityayadav4507/Inventory-Management-Application.git
```

---

## Move Into Project Directory

```bash
cd Inventory-Management-Application
```

---

## Run Full Application Using Docker

```bash
docker-compose up --build
```

---

# ⚙️ Environment Variables

## Backend Environment Variables

```env
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:password@db:5432/inventory
```

---

# 📡 API Endpoints

## Products

| Method | Endpoint         | Description           |
| ------ | ---------------- | --------------------- |
| GET    | `/products`      | Retrieve all products |
| POST   | `/products`      | Create product        |
| PUT    | `/products/{id}` | Update product        |
| DELETE | `/products/{id}` | Delete product        |

---

## Customers

| Method | Endpoint          | Description        |
| ------ | ----------------- | ------------------ |
| GET    | `/customers`      | Retrieve customers |
| POST   | `/customers`      | Create customer    |
| DELETE | `/customers/{id}` | Delete customer    |

---

## Orders

| Method | Endpoint       | Description         |
| ------ | -------------- | ------------------- |
| GET    | `/orders`      | Retrieve orders     |
| POST   | `/orders`      | Create order        |
| DELETE | `/orders/{id}` | Cancel/Delete order |

---

## Dashboard

| Method | Endpoint             | Description         |
| ------ | -------------------- | ------------------- |
| GET    | `/dashboard/summary` | Dashboard analytics |

---

